                    </div>
                    <p class="text-[9px] text-slate-400 mt-2">※ 你的 Key 僅會儲存在手機本地，不會上傳至他人伺服器。</p>
                </div>

                <div class="space-y-4 mt-6">
                    <div id="pwa-install-btn" class="manhua-card flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer bg-yellow-400 hidden">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-download text-xl"></i>
                            <span class="font-black text-sm">將「絕世帳簿」安裝至手機</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="manhua-card flex items-center justify-between p-4 cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-50">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <i class="fas fa-scroll text-xl text-red-600"></i>
                            <span class="font-black text-sm">傳音入密 (通知)</span>
                        </div>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-right text-slate-400"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center py-4">
                        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-300 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Version 1.1.0-MANHUA-PWA</p>
